_sText:
This is a map project for this Halloween. It is a office map with a FEAR theme. The map has been edited and is now at least twice as large as cs_office_extended which is the base for this project. First thing i should note is despite all my attempts at opting this map, i couldn't get the map to compile under full vis which would get stuck every time, so the map is fast vis. If that doesn't bother you then enjoy.
